Responsive Grid System

Makes websites adjust automatically on different screen sizes (mobile, tablet, desktop).

Based on 12 columns.

Pre-styled Components

Buttons, cards, navbars, forms, modals, carousels, alerts, etc., ready to use.

Built-in CSS Classes

For spacing, typography, colors, alignment, etc.
Example: text-center, bg-primary, mt-4, etc.

JavaScript Plugins

Interactive components like dropdowns, tooltips, modals, and tabs, using jQuery or Bootstrapâ€™s JS.

Customization

You can customize Bootstrap with SASS variables or by overriding CSS.
